Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite this "Mirror World."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same way Kanbaru's arm was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't being mirrored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't being reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait. Don't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My visual confirmation has a limit.
